<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 01 at 8:57PM CST  by NWS Midland-Odessa</headline>
<description>...Winter precipitation reported across parts of Southeast New
Mexico and the Permian Basin...
Light snow, sleet, mixed with some rain has been reported from Lea
County New Mexico eastward to Scurry County and as far south as
the Midland/Odessa. New Mexico DOT reports some difficult driving
conditions in the Tatum area with snow and some ice on roads.
Elsewhere accumulations will be lighter, still a few slick spots
may develop across the mentioned areas. All precipitation types
are expected to end by 1 AM CST.
Use caution if driving on this very cold night.</description>
